# GDPR Compliance (Conditional)

Apply these rules if EU personal data is processed.

## Requirements
- Minimize collection; document lawful basis for processing.
- Support data access and deletion requests via a documented procedure.
- Keep data localized to the user device unless explicit consent and safeguards exist.
- Maintain retention limits and purge paths consistent with GDPR principles.

## Notes
- HIPAA requirements still apply to PHI; GDPR does not replace HIPAA obligations.
